"{\"uid\": \"indianewengland.com-paris-olympics-vinesh-phogat-gets-her-redemption-one-bout-at-a-time\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"New Delhi- As she along with Bajrang Punia and Sakshi Malik led the protests against Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh, the ousted president of the Wrestling Federation of India (WFI), Vinesh Phogat has become one of the most hated sportspersons in the country, facing online abuse daily from a section of the netizens.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bajrang Punia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\"}, {\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0692020400664464e-31, \"text\": \"Sakshi Malik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\"}, {\"begin\": 177, \"end\": 190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"New Delhi-\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 10}, {\"ngram\": \"the protests\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 76}, {\"ngram\": \"Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 110}, {\"ngram\": \"the ousted president\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wrestling Federation\", \"from\": 136, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"India\", \"from\": 164, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 174}, {\"ngram\": \"the most hated sportspersons\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 237}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 241, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"online abuse\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 273}, {\"ngram\": \"a section\", \"from\": 285, \"to\": 294}, {\"ngram\": \"the netizens\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was vilified when she raised her voice against some of the moves by the WFI, and she was abused when she came down from 53 kg weight class to 50 kg and participated in two weight categories in the trials seeking guarantees from WFI officials.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her voice\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"the moves\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"53 kg weight class\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"50 kg\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"two weight categories\", \"from\": 485, \"to\": 506}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 520}, {\"ngram\": \"guarantees\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI officials\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the tacit support of the administrators, Vinesh was painted as a villain who was trying to gain favours and a backdoor entry into the team.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 606, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tacit support\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"the administrators\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"a villain\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"favours\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 668}, {\"ngram\": \"a backdoor entry\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even her own cousins had turned against Vinesh as a section of the media and netizens went after the two-time Olympian, depicting her as a spent force who is always depending on her past achievements.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 746, \"end\": 752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"netizens\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netizen\"}, {\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999997953637, \"rank\": 2.0456703159885151e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even her own cousins\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"a section\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 765}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"a spent force\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"her past achievements\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, the 29-year-old grappler from Haryana silenced her critics and abusers with two brilliant performances that took her into the semifinals of the women's 50kg weight class at the Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 950, \"end\": 957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999907531674, \"rank\": 9.246897819613637e-09, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"the 29-year-old grappler\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"her critics\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"abusers\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"two brilliant performances\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"the semifinals\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's 50kg weight class\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1116}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh first upset World No.1 Yui Susaki of Japan in the pre-quarterfinal and got the better of Ukraine's Oksana Vasylivna Livach 7-5 in the last-eight stage to storm into the semifinals.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1163, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9967377964629079, \"rank\": 0.003167223139024108, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1215, \"end\": 1222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 7.548296230520607e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vinesh\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"World No.1 Yui Susaki\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"Livach\", \"from\": 1242, \"to\": 1248}, {\"ngram\": \"the last-eight stage\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"the semifinals\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The former World No.1 in 48kg weight made a stunning debut in the 50kg class in the Olympics with a shocking win against four-time World Champion and Tokyo Olympic Games bronze medallist Yui Susaki of Japan.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1439, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"score\": 0.9914998133389722, \"rank\": 0.008567504696071586, \"text\": \"World Champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\"}, {\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yui Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\"}, {\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9967377964629079, \"rank\": 0.003167223139024108, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The former World No.1\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"48kg weight\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunning debut\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50kg class\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"a shocking win\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Playing against the undisputed queen in 50 kg, Vinesh defended strongly, not allowing the Japanese grappler a chance to attack and effect a take-down.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9905931895316293, \"rank\": 0.009310555501978677, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the undisputed queen\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"50 kg\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"a take-down\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was twice penalised a point each for passivity but did not lose her cool.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"passivity\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She launched a lightning-fast attack in the last 20 seconds and made a take-down to gain three points and win the bout.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lightning-fast attack\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 20 seconds\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"a take-down\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"three points\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An hour later, Vinesh quelled the challenge of Ukraine's Oksana Vasylivna Livach 7-5 in her second bout of the day.\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1882, \"end\": 1888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 1914, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999904503, \"rank\": 7.548296230520607e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the challenge\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"her second bout\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1974, \"to\": 1981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh took an initial lead of 2-0 in the first period of the match against Oksana, who won her first bout 10-0 on technical superiority.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vinesh\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"an initial lead\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"the first period\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2051}, {\"ngram\": \"Oksana\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"her first bout\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2090}, {\"ngram\": \"technical superiority\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second period was a bit challenging for Vinesh as Oksana fought back and took a 2-pointer after the Indian grappler had stretched her lead to 4-0 with two minutes and two seconds remaining in the match.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 2226, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.5896719615193643, \"rank\": 0.38129137872501895, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The second period\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"Oksana\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"a 2-pointer\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"her lead\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2264}, {\"ngram\": \"two minutes\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"two seconds\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh recovered quickly to counter and got one more point to her name to take the lead 5-2.\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vinesh\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2336}, {\"ngram\": \"one more point\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2388}, {\"ngram\": \"her name\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the last few seconds of the bout, the Ukrainian attacked fiercely but Vinesh managed to hold on to her defence and counter-attacked to get a 2-pointer via technical superiority.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2464, \"end\": 2473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999991848654, \"rank\": 8.008545456509236e-10, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 2496, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the last few seconds\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"the bout\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"her defence\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"counter\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"a 2-pointer\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2576}, {\"ngram\": \"technical superiority\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But life before the Paris Olympic Games was quite tough for Vinesh as every move of hers was questioned and disputed as she had stood against the regimen and supported the wrestlers in their protest against Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh for alleged sexual harassment of young female wrestlers.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"every move\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2685}, {\"ngram\": \"the regimen\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"their protest\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"alleged sexual harassment\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2867}, {\"ngram\": \"young female wrestlers\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(IANS) Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment.\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2896, \"end\": 2900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indo-Asian_News_Service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IANS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indo-Asian_News_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indo-Asian_News_Service\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"email\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"website\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"this browser\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"the next time\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\":